49:16.164 --> 49:17.165
I know you.

49:18.876 --> 49:21.962
And you are not your biggest mistake.

49:23.422 --> 49:28.969
Damn, Coach. That really means something.

49:28.969 --> 49:30.095
I'm glad.

49:36.518 --> 49:37.561
All right.

49:37.561 --> 49:40.147
- I got about six more months.
- Aight, bet.

49:40.147 --> 49:41.607
I mean, you already got it,

49:41.607 --> 49:45.485
but you can use this last bit of time
to just train, train, train.

49:45.485 --> 49:47.863
- By the time you out of here...
- Nah.

49:48.488 --> 49:50.157
My basketball days, man.

49:51.825 --> 49:54.494
Look, I don't do well with stress.

49:55.037 --> 49:57.789
Looks like you handled all the stress
out there today pretty well.

49:57.789 --> 50:00.167
Man, that? Man, that was light work.

50:00.876 --> 50:02.044
You shouldn't play with me.

50:02.711 --> 50:03.795
He called us light work.

50:04.796 --> 50:06.715
Y'all ever heard of South Plains College?

50:07.883 --> 50:11.345
That's a juco in Texas.
Got some good things going on over there.

50:11.845 --> 50:13.972
They wanna take a look at me
after I get out.

50:14.556 --> 50:16.058
That's what's up. And congrats on that.

50:16.058 --> 50:19.520
Thank you.
You think y'all can put in a word?

50:19.520 --> 50:23.524
With your hops and your nasty defense?
You got my word.

50:24.858 --> 50:29.988
Hey, team. Y'all gonna put
a dollar in my phone account?

50:30.614 --> 50:31.448
Here you go.

50:31.448 --> 50:32.741
Always begging for some shit.

50:32.741 --> 50:34.159
I'm for real.

50:34.159 --> 50:36.828
I bet a week's worth
of calls on this game.

50:37.329 --> 50:38.872
I can't not call my family for a week.

50:39.831 --> 50:41.333
And what does that have to do with us?

50:41.333 --> 50:44.378
Everything. What you mean?
I got into this by losing.

50:44.378 --> 50:46.588
Hey, man,
I'll put three dollars on there, bro.

50:47.214 --> 50:48.632
Thanks, D.

50:49.299 --> 50:51.969
Hey, Vince, what about you?

50:53.971 --> 50:57.599
I gotta check my account,
make sure my mom's wire came through.

50:57.599 --> 50:58.684
Sergeant Hampton?

50:59.726 --> 51:03.355
Hypothetically, if a visitor wanted
to put some money on someone's account

51:03.355 --> 51:06.149
so they could use the phone,
is that possible?

51:06.900 --> 51:09.194
Hypothetically, yes.

51:09.194 --> 51:12.155
On the way out,
visitors can stop by account services.

51:14.074 --> 51:15.450
It's a bug in my food.

51:16.201 --> 51:19.037
Who put that shit in there, huh?
Who did it?

51:19.037 --> 51:20.205
- Yo, D, chill.
- Relax, man.

51:20.205 --> 51:22.833
- We can get you another tray.
- Man, I'm not even hungry anymore.

51:22.833 --> 51:25.294
You know,
that's probably what they wanted too.

51:25.294 --> 51:27.796
- Have me starve after the game.
- Hey.

51:28.839 --> 51:31.466
Man, that's some straight up bullshit.

51:31.466 --> 51:33.177
- Hey!
- Yo, relax.

51:33.177 --> 51:34.094
- Come on.
- What?

51:34.094 --> 51:36.305
- Deandre, sit down.
- They always messing with me in here!

51:37.055 --> 51:40.058
- Why is that?
- Deandre, calm down.

51:40.058 --> 51:42.978
What-- Man, let me go. Let-- Get off me.

51:42.978 --> 51:45.397
- No. What are you doing?
- Yo! What are you doing?

51:45.397 --> 51:48.025
- That's not necessary. Let him go.
- Back up. This is for his own protection.

51:48.025 --> 51:50.277
- This some bullshit.
- Jace, that's enough!

51:52.112 --> 51:52.988
Man.

51:56.241 --> 51:57.659
Don't let them do this to you.

51:59.286 --> 52:01.663
Don't let them take your heart from you,
Jace Carson.

52:03.123 --> 52:06.793
If they think they can... they will!

52:09.338 --> 52:11.965
They've been putting me
on medication since I was 12.

52:13.759 --> 52:15.135
But I keep fighting.

52:16.303 --> 52:18.263
I keep fighting!

52:26.188 --> 52:27.189
Jace.

52:47.626 --> 52:49.920
This is not the way
I hoped the day would end.

52:51.088 --> 52:54.174
I wanna thank you guys.
Appreciate what you did.

52:55.342 --> 52:57.719
More than you'll ever know. Thank you.

53:36.466 --> 53:38.427
In this room right here
to your right, son.

53:57.196 --> 53:58.197
Pop.

54:01.783 --> 54:02.784
Hey.

54:06.997 --> 54:07.998
I...

54:10.834 --> 54:14.129
I haven't been
wearing my kufi like I used to do.

54:14.129 --> 54:19.051
I noticed. But you don't
gotta rock a kufi to be a good Muslim.

54:22.095 --> 54:23.180
I know. It's just...

54:25.807 --> 54:27.935
after everything that happened...

54:30.646 --> 54:32.189
I didn't know what I believed.

54:33.482 --> 54:34.483
I get it.

54:39.112 --> 54:44.409
You know, you told me
that I was here for a reason.

54:45.160 --> 54:46.161
Yes.

54:46.912 --> 54:49.081
You told me I can make a difference.

54:52.960 --> 54:54.294
And if I lose faith in that?

54:54.920 --> 54:56.338
We lose everything.

54:59.216 --> 55:00.968
I really wanna make dua right now.

55:04.137 --> 55:05.138
Me too, Son.

55:10.269 --> 55:11.645
<i>Bismillah.</i>

55:13.272 --> 55:14.273
<i>Bismillah.</i>

55:20.696 --> 55:23.532
We praise you, Allah.
We beseech you, Allah.

56:00.527 --> 56:01.528
You okay?

56:05.782 --> 56:06.783
I just felt rain.

56:15.709 --> 56:16.710
Let's hit the road.

56:29.556 --> 56:30.557
Hello.

56:34.728 --> 56:35.729
You sure?

56:37.564 --> 56:38.857
Hold on.

56:43.570 --> 56:46.365
Okay, can you text that to me?

56:47.866 --> 56:49.201
All right.

56:52.955 --> 56:54.915
I just got off the phone
with Alonzo Powers.

56:54.915 --> 56:59.127
He connected with some of your parents,
and the DA decided not to charge you.

57:01.338 --> 57:04.216
They're gonna want community service

57:04.216 --> 57:06.009
but there's no jail time.

57:07.302 --> 57:11.723
And "the Maryland Unified Athletic Council

57:11.723 --> 57:14.059
has suspended you
from all basketball endeavors."

57:15.894 --> 57:19.690
"However,
if you apologize for your actions...

57:21.942 --> 57:23.527
you'll be immediately reinstated."

57:28.532 --> 57:29.533
You're free.

57:41.628 --> 57:42.629
Let's go home.

58:04.943 --> 58:07.863
Let's go!

58:10.824 --> 58:13.493
Yeah, it's raining! Wash it all away!

58:13.493 --> 58:18.373
Wash it all away! It's raining! Let's go!

58:18.373 --> 58:20.459
- Okay, Nico. Let's go.
- Let's go!

58:22.544 --> 58:26.548
Let's go! Yeah!
